indictment and

19:04.977 --> 19:09.381 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
what the Senate would say in
whether to convict
on that bill.

19:09.414 --> 19:12.417 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
MICHAEL WALDMAN: I do think
that's exactly
right.

19:12.451 --> 19:17.256 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
You had, for example, during
