ties between
the nations' intelligence
services?

49:05.642 --> 49:07.477 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
For that, we turn to Ronen
Bergman.

49:07.511 --> 49:12.849 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
He's the intelligence
correspondent for Israel's
largest daily newspaper, Yedioth
Ahronoth.

49:12.883 --> 49:17.688 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
His forthcoming book is called
"Rise and Kill
First: The Secret History of
Israel's Targeted

49:17.721 --> 49:18.822 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
Assassinations."

49:18.855 --> 49:20.857 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
And he joins me now from Tel
Aviv.

49:20.891 --> 49:26.630 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Ronen, may I first ask you, were
you able
to confirm that this
intelligence that the

49:26.663 --> 49:31.268 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
president allegedly divulged was
in fact from
Israel, and, if so, what the
reaction among

49:31.301 --> 49:32.869 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
Israeli intelligence has been?

49:32.903 --> 49:37.341 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
RONEN BERGMAN, Analyst, Yedioth
Ahronoth:
This is not yet finally
confirmed.

49:37.374 --> 49:42.879 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
There's an investigation going
on in Israel,
trying to check which of the
many, many items

49:42.913 --> 49:46.516 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
of intelligence that was
delivered to the
United States during the last
three or four

49:46.550 --> 49:55.726 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
months regarding Syria, the
activity of ISIS,
Russia, Hezbollah, Iran, all
closely guarded

49:55.759 --> 50:02.199 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
by Israel, which of these items
were given
by President Trump to Foreign
Minister Lavrov.

50:02.232 --> 50:08.805 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
As per the emotions or the
reactions inside
Israeli intelligence community,
I would say

50:08.839 --> 50:11.108 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
they are ballistic.

50:11.141 --> 50:15.112 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
There are many people who are
extremely upset.

50:15.145 --> 50:22.552 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And one of them told me, this is
sort of -- this
is a kick, violation in our
sacred trust of

50:22.586 --> 50:27.991 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
each other, a blunt violation of
everything
the two countries agreed.

50:28.025 --> 50:35.265 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
That person said that maybe the
president
has an authority, as he tweeted,
to deliver

50:35.298 --> 50:40.604 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
U.S. intelligence, but he
doesn't have any
authority to share Israeli
intelligence and

50:40.637 --> 50:44.708 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
intelligence that was shared
with these close
circles of Americans, and just
Americans,

50:44.741 --> 50:46.076 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
with anyone else.

50:46.109 --> 50:48.812 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: President
Trump spoke with
Netanyahu yesterday.

50:48.845 --> 50:51.581 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
