part of that
conversation.

50:51.615 --> 50:57.721 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
RONEN BERGMAN: Well, I don't
know what was
said or not said during that
conversation.

50:57.754 --> 51:04.861 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
