Netanyahu ordered
his staff not to react in any
way to the recent

51:04.895 --> 51:09.866 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
scandals in the United States,
including the
leakage of information, Israeli
intelligence

51:09.900 --> 51:11.635 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
to the Russians.

51:11.668 --> 51:18.208 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
