intelligence sources,
as much as possible.

52:10.527 --> 52:18.068 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
If, indeed, information that is
in the hands
of U.S. intelligence, U.S.
National Security

52:18.101 --> 52:26.309 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Council, U.S. president is not
safe, that
means that much of the secrets
of Israel,

52:26.343 --> 52:31.314 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
