at risk.

52:37.654 --> 52:45.362 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And one of the Israeli officials
told me that
he believes that there needs to
be a reassessment

52:45.395 --> 52:51.535 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
of everything that was -- that
will be delivered
to the U.S. from this point on,
until it's

52:51.568 --> 52:56.773 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
proven that the channel, this
pipeline of
information going from Israel to
the United

52:56.806 --> 53:02.879 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
States, and vice versa, of
course, is safe
again and can be trusted 100
percent.

53:02.913 --> 53:06.183 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Nothing less than 100 percent is
not secure.

53:06.216 --> 53:09.920 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: All right,
Ronen Bergman,
thank you very, very much for
your time.

53:09.953 --> 53:11.221 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
RONEN BERGMAN: Thank you.

